landingPage.introduction:
You already looked for a Curriculum Vitae of a Software Engineer?
Why so many times recruiters ask for a traditional CV for a software engineer role?
If you are an IT specialist why your are not building your own platform to show your work and your skills?

Turn a boring task for IT recruiters, an experience close to the technologie and softare implementation.

Developed by @ Emanuel Teixeira
